        "little",
        "overhead",
        "possible"
      ]
    },
    {
      "ruleId": "hz.web.44116608b5710af8.rule.3",
      "text": "Then, as you’re developing, when a test or assertion fails, QUnit should provide feedback to you as fast as possible, with enough detail to quickly figure out the underlying issue.",
      "tokens": [
        "then",
        "re",
        "developing",
        "test",
        "assertion",
        "fails",
        "qunit",
